---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const faqSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Do you offer emergency plumbing in Cardinia Lakes?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes &mdash; we run a 24/7 emergency plumber service across Cardinia Lakes 3810 for burst pipes, sewer overflows, gas leaks and no hot water. As an early-2000s estate, Cardinia Lakes has plenty of ageing pipework and original hot water units, so winter emergency call-outs here are common. Call (03) 9003 0108 any time." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Why do drains block so often in Cardinia Lakes?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Cardinia Lakes was built out in the early 2000s and its street and garden trees are now 15-20 years old. The roots have reached the clay-bedded sewer and stormwater lines and are causing the estate's first real wave of root-intrusion blockages. We CCTV the line to find the exact entry point, hydro-jet and cut the roots, and can reline a cracked pipe without digging." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "My Cardinia Lakes hot water unit is about 15 years old &mdash; should I replace it?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Very likely. The original hot water units across Cardinia Lakes are now in the 10-15 year replacement window and are failing in batches. If yours gives rusty water, pools at the base, knocks, or runs cold quickly, replace it before it fails on a cold morning. We can do a same-day like-for-like changeover with a tempering valve and Certificate of Compliance, typically around $2,100 fitted." }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Question",
      "name": "Are you licensed to work in Cardinia Lakes?",
      "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes &mdash; we are VBA-licensed plumbers working to AS/NZS 3500 (and AS/NZS 5601 for gas) and we issue a Certificate of Compliance on prescribed work, meeting South East Water connection and backflow requirements under the Victorian Plumbing Regulations 2018." }
    }
  ]
};
---
<Layout
  title="Plumber Cardinia Lakes | Emergency, Hot Water, Drains | (03) 9003 0108"
  canonical="https://pakenhamplumbers.com.au/cardinia-lakes/"
  description="Local plumber for Cardinia Lakes 3810 &mdash; 24/7 emergency, blocked drains, hot water replacement, burst pipes &amp; gas fitting. Early-2000s estate specialists: ageing units &amp; the first wave of tree-root drain blockages. VBA-licensed.">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(faqSchema)} />
  </Fragment>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Cardinia Lakes &middot; 3810</span>
      <h1>Plumber in <span class="accent">Cardinia Lakes</span>.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Cardinia Lakes is one of Pakenham&rsquo;s big early-2000s estates &mdash; and that
        age shows in the plumbing. Hot water units are hitting the 10&ndash;15 year
        replacement window, fixtures are ageing, and the estate&rsquo;s maturing trees are
        driving the first real wave of blocked-drain call-outs. We handle all of it.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Why Cardinia Lakes</span>
      <h2>The Cardinia Lakes plumbing story.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>
      <div style="max-width: 65rem;">
        <h3>An estate hitting its replacement window.</h3>
        <p>
          Built out in the early 2000s, Cardinia Lakes is now 15 to 20 years old. The
          original gas and electric hot water units installed when the estate went up are
          built to last 10&ndash;15 years &mdash; which is exactly where they are now,
          failing in batches especially on cold winter mornings. We carry the common
          Rheem, Rinnai, Dux and Aquamax units and can usually do a same-day
          <a href="/services/hot-water-systems/">hot water replacement</a> with a tempering
          valve and Certificate of Compliance, typically around $2,100 fitted.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">The first wave of tree-root drains.</h3>
        <p>
          The fast-growing street and garden trees planted when Cardinia Lakes was built
          are now mature, and their roots have reached the clay-bedded sewer and
          stormwater lines. That is driving the estate&rsquo;s first real wave of
          <a href="/services/blocked-drains/">blocked drains</a> &mdash; roots mat up at a
          joint and trap grease and wipes. We CCTV the line to find the exact entry point,
          hydro-jet and cut the roots, and where the pipe is cracked we can reline it
          without digging up the yard.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Ageing fixtures &amp; pipework.</h3>
        <p>
          Twenty years on, the original tapware, toilet cisterns, flexi-hoses and copper
          are reaching the end of their seal life. We see worn mixers, running toilets,
          weeping connections and the occasional burst flexi-hose &mdash; the last one a
          common cause of indoor flooding. We recommend replacing braided flexi-hoses
          every 5&ndash;7 years before they let go.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Typical Cardinia Lakes jobs.</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Same-day hot water unit changeover (gas or electric) &mdash; ~$1,400&ndash;$2,600</li>
          <li>Tree-root blocked sewer: CCTV + hydro-jet + root cut &mdash; ~$450&ndash;$650</li>
          <li>Burst flexi-hose flooding under a sink &mdash; 24/7 emergency call-out</li>
          <li>Tap, toilet and mixer replacements as the estate&rsquo;s fixtures age</li>
          <li><a href="/services/gas-fitting/">Gas appliance</a> connections and CO testing on older heaters</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Other service areas.</h2>
      <div class="areas-grid">
        <a class="area-pill" href="/lakeside/">Lakeside</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/heritage-springs/">Heritage Springs</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/officer/">Officer</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/beaconsfield/">Beaconsfield</a>
        <a class="area-pill" href="/cardinia-shire/">All Cardinia Shire</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Need a plumber in Cardinia Lakes?</h2>
        <p>Emergency or everyday. Same-day hot water, drain clearing, gas fitting &mdash; all with a CoC.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030108">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0108</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
